    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine. This specimen boasts a robust power band with the VANOS system recently serviced for optimal variable valve timing performance. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The suspension retains its factory geometry, delivering precise feedback through the rack-and-pinion steering. While the aesthetic reflects its status as a well-loved driver's car, the drivetrain remains in peak operational form, free of fluid leaks or rod bearing noise.",
