    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Executive Sport Sedan that perfectly balances performance and comfort. This vehicle has been my reliable daily driver and is in great shape for its mileage. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, though there are a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small, superficial scuff on the rear passenger-side bumper\u2014hardly noticeable from a distance but worth mentioning for total transparency. Inside, the premium charcoal leather interior is clean and free of tears; the driver\u2019s seat shows only light softening on the side bolster. All electronic features, including the panoramic sunroof, dual-zone climate control, and the premium 12-speaker sound system, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is sound. It has a full service history with the most recent oil and filter change completed just 500 miles ago. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brake pads were replaced last spring. It shifts smoothly and provides a quiet, confident ride. Includes two sets of keys and all original owner manuals. This is a solid, honest car ready for its next owner.",
